        "Description": [
          {
            "text": "This reusable travel tumbler carrier holder pouch is crafted from high-quality neoprene, offering durability and eco-friendliness for environmentally conscious users. It provides excellent insulation, keeping both hot and cold beverages at optimal temperatures, making it ideal for iced coffee in summer or warm drinks in winter. The versatile design fits various cup sizes snugly, ensuring a secure and comfortable grip. Its lightweight and portable nature makes it perfect for home, office, or on-the-go use like travel, camping, or classroom settings. With a sleek, modern style, it adds a touch of flair to your drink. Suitable for promotional purposes, it can be customized with logos, making it a great wholesale or bulk branded item. Compatible with popular bottle types, this neoprene sleeve is a practical and sustainable accessory for anyone needing to keep their drinks at the right temperature while on the move. Rush service is available for quick fulfillment.",
            "type": "text"
          }
