        "备注": "[\"杯子配件\"]",
        "完整描述": "Made from high quality neoprene material, this cup sleeve is designed to be reusable, making it an eco - friendly choice for the environmentally conscious consumers. Whether you're a fan of iced coffee on a hot summer day or prefer to keep your hot drinks warm during the chilly winter months, this cup sleeve has got you covered. It provides excellent insulation for both hot and cold beverages, ensuring that your drink stays at the perfect temperature for longer. The cup sleeve is specifically designed to fit a wide variety of cup sizes, making it extremely versatile. It snugly wraps around your cup, providing a comfortable and secure grip. With its sleek and modern design, it adds a touch of style to your drink. It's perfect for use at home, in the office, or on the go.",
